{
  "id": "698af2311e7409dc6ebf2699",
  "title": "下線に色をつけるUserCSS",
  "created": 1770713652,
  "updated": 1771114641,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "698af2311e7409dc6ebf2699",
      "text": "下線に色をつけるUserCSS",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713652,
      "updated": 1770713652
    },
    {
      "id": "698af23300000000009778d7",
      "text": "動機",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713652,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778d8",
      "text": "3色ボールペンみたいに色をつけて下線をいれたい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778d9",
      "text": "重要な箇所には赤のアンダーライン、面白いと思った箇所には緑のアンダーライン、というように、目的によってアンダーラインの色を使い分ける",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778da",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778db",
      "text": "[/customize/マーカー記法]を参考にした（ほぼパクリ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778dc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778dd",
      "text": "code:style.css",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778de",
      "text": " .deco-\\_ {",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778df",
      "text": "   text-decoration: underline solid ; /* アンダーライン */",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778e0",
      "text": "   text-decoration-thickness: 2px; /* 線の太さ */",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778e1",
      "text": "   text-decoration-color: var(--page-text-color, black); /* */",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770714748
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778e2",
      "text": "   &:has(span:nth-child(1) > a[data-page-title=\"blue\"]) {",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778e3",
      "text": "     text-decoration-color: lightblue;/* */",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778e4",
      "text": "     & > span:nth-child(1) > a { display: none; }",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778e5",
      "text": "   }",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778e6",
      "text": "   &:has(span:nth-child(1) > a[data-page-title=\"red\"]) {",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778e7",
      "text": "     text-decoration-color: red;/* */",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778e8",
      "text": "     & > span:nth-child(1) > a { display: none; }",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778e9",
      "text": "   }",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778ea",
      "text": "   &:has(span:nth-child(1) > a[data-page-title=\"green\"]) {",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778eb",
      "text": "     text-decoration-color: green;/* */",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778ec",
      "text": "     & > span:nth-child(1) > a { display: none; }",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778ed",
      "text": "   }",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778ee",
      "text": "   &:has(span:nth-child(1) > a[data-page-title=\"yellow\"]) {",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778ef",
      "text": "     text-decoration-color: yellow;/* */",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778f0",
      "text": "     text-decoration-thickness: 4px; /* 線の太さ */",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778f1",
      "text": "     & > span:nth-child(1) > a { display: none; }",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778f2",
      "text": "   }    ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778f3",
      "text": "   &:has(span:nth-child(1) > a[data-page-title=\"black\"]) {",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778f4",
      "text": "     text-decoration-color: black;/* */",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778f5",
      "text": "     & > span:nth-child(1) > a { display: none; }",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778f6",
      "text": "   }    ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778f7",
      "text": " }",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af25d00000000009778f8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1770713693,
      "updated": 1770713693
    },
    {
      "id": "698af6580000000000a2bfc4",
      "text": "んー、下線記法はHTMLがなんか特殊で、DOMにstyleが直接書かれているのよね…[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770714714,
      "updated": 1770718477
    },
    {
      "id": "698af6390000000000a2bfc2",
      "text": "\tcode:下線の.HTML",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770714683,
      "updated": 1770714720
    },
    {
      "id": "698af60f0000000000a2bfc0",
      "text": "\t\t<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770714642,
      "updated": 1770714726
    },
    {
      "id": "698af6650000000000a2bfc5",
      "text": "\t\t\t<span class=\"deco-_\">",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770714727,
      "updated": 1770714740
    },
    {
      "id": "698af6740000000000a2bfc6",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t<...>",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770714742,
      "updated": 1770714751
    },
    {
      "id": "698af67e0000000000a2bfc7",
      "text": "\t\t\t</span>",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770714752,
      "updated": 1770714756
    },
    {
      "id": "698af6840000000000a2bfc8",
      "text": "\t\t</span>",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770714759,
      "updated": 1770715889
    },
    {
      "id": "698af64f0000000000a2bfc3",
      "text": " ああいや、元のままでもとくに不都合ないのか",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770715889,
      "updated": 1770718185
    },
    {
      "id": "698af94c0000000000acc5e8",
      "text": "\t自分は自分のProjectで下線を波線に変えようとして引っかかったんですよね",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770715470,
      "updated": 1770716344
    },
    {
      "id": "698af7c70000000000baa116",
      "text": "あともし将来的に[大きなリンク]になって関連ページリストの 2-hop link が鬱陶しくなるようだったら、関連ページリストから非表示にしたくなるかもしれない（[& 元の[/customize/マーカー記法]の作者自身の経験談]）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770715081,
      "updated": 1770718210
    },
    {
      "id": "698af9ca0000000000acc5e9",
      "text": "\tので簡単にオン・オフできるようにUserCSSをあらかじめ設置しておこう",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770715597,
      "updated": 1770715988
    },
    {
      "id": "698b00560000000000acc61b",
      "text": "\t\tこれは[/customize]のほうにも注意書きをいれるべきだな…",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770717272,
      "updated": 1770717625
    },
    {
      "id": "698afdf40000000000acc615",
      "text": "\tあとテキストのロールと色分けの関係性は自明でないという問題がある",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770716662,
      "updated": 1770716699
    },
    {
      "id": "698afe6e0000000000acc617",
      "text": " \t対処としては、リンク名や文字装飾の意図が[セマンティック]に伝えられるようにあのUserCSSを改変すること",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770716784,
      "updated": 1770717656
    },
    {
      "id": "698afe190000000000acc616",
      "text": " \t\t仮に[\" 重要な箇所には赤のアンダーライン]を引くのだったら赤線が引かれるリンク名を`[important]`にするとか",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770716699,
      "updated": 1770717372
    },
    {
      "id": "698b002f0000000000acc61a",
      "text": " \t\t`::before`/`::after`疑似要素で別途記号を表示するとかですね",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770717233,
      "updated": 1770723958
    },
    {
      "id": "698affe20000000000acc619",
      "text": "  \t\t[色盲]対応にもなる",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770717156,
      "updated": 1770720189
    },
    {
      "id": "698afa3f0000000000acc609",
      "text": "関連ページリストの 2-hop link を無効にするUserCSS",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770715713,
      "updated": 1770716123
    },
    {
      "id": "698afa370000000000acc607",
      "text": " code:style.css",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770715705,
      "updated": 1770715705
    },
    {
      "id": "698afa3d0000000000acc608",
      "text": "\tcode:disabled",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770715711,
      "updated": 1770715954
    },
    {
      "id": "698afa2d0000000000acc5fb",
      "text": "  .related-page-list .links-2-hop:has(",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770715695,
      "updated": 1770715695
    },
    {
      "id": "698afa2d0000000000acc5fc",
      "text": "  \ta[href=\"/villagepump/blue\"],",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770715695,
      "updated": 1770715806
    },
    {
      "id": "698afabf0000000000acc60c",
      "text": "  \ta[href=\"/villagepump/red\"],",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770715841,
      "updated": 1770715841
    },
    {
      "id": "698afa2d0000000000acc5ff",
      "text": "  \ta[href=\"/villagepump/green\"],",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770715695,
      "updated": 1770715826
    },
    {
      "id": "698afac50000000000acc612",
      "text": "  \ta[href=\"/villagepump/yellow\"],",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770715847,
      "updated": 1770715847
    },
    {
      "id": "698afac70000000000acc614",
      "text": "  \ta[href=\"/villagepump/black\"]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770715849,
      "updated": 1770715854
    },
    {
      "id": "698afa2d0000000000acc602",
      "text": "\t\t) {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770715695,
      "updated": 1770715695
    },
    {
      "id": "698afa2d0000000000acc603",
      "text": "  \tdisplay: none !important;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770715695,
      "updated": 1770715695
    },
    {
      "id": "698afa2d0000000000acc604",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770715695,
      "updated": 1770715695
    },
    {
      "id": "698afa2d0000000000acc605",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1770715695,
      "updated": 1770715695
    },
    {
